    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/7930910356cbf83da411627592e6506f.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/fbf64feb64dacb5d9aa88140c5e1da55.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>&quot;纪律神殿供奉着纪律女神乌迪安娜…<br>然而，在女神的冷漠中，他们一一消失了。&quot;<br><br>&quot;而在安达伦这里，仅存的最后一座秩序神殿，也因为叛徒之墓的不死生物而遭到袭击。&quot;<br><br>&quot;从今以后，一切都是他们的终结…&quot;<br><br>仅存的最后一名牧师克莱尔决定冒着生命危险与士兵们一起对抗不死生物，为村民们安全撤离。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/333dca954c946eafbcc82ea31bbfd524.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>亡灵的进攻开始了。<br>聚集圣力召唤士兵，强化海伦迪尔的星光打败亡灵。<br>如果亡灵赢了，游戏就结束了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/517989f214d683cc12de9aa63fd81870.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>▷ 迷人的角色<br>▷ 人物塔防<br>▷ 游戏模式：故事模式、无尽模式<br>▷ 玩游戏时可以解锁的各种皮肤和特殊物品<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280540/extras/35db10148608faf464042880d81a89a9.avif?t=1747123601\" width=616 height=400 /></span>",
